<div style="width: 80%; margin: 2em auto;">
<p class="content">Welcome to the Executive Suite Program.  We at Republic Technologies are pleased to offer you an exclusive sneak peek into what we have worked so hard to develop over the past 18 months.  I would like to take this time to offer you a brief introduction into what you will find in this great new tool for your office!  Please feel free to contact us at <a href="mailto:esuite@republictech.net">esuite@republictech.net</a> with any questions you may have.</p>

<h2 class="subheader">Inventory Management</h2>
<p class="content">This advanced inventory tracking system features customizable product and accessory types with variable inventory status options.   As a inventory item is sold, the status of the item will automatically change from checked in to sold.  In addition, this section features a fully functional search and filtration system to easily locate information on any inventory item that you need.</p>

<h2 class="subheader">Sales Management</h2>
<p class="content">Sales are the most important aspect of yourk business and as a result we spent a lot of time hammering out this section.  But it is far from perfect.  As a beta participant we need your help to hammer out all those finer details of a Kirby Sale.   However, we do have a lot of great features in this section including:</>
<ul>
	<li class="content">Grid based list of all sales</li>
	<li class="content">Innovative filtration system </li>
	<li class="content">Detailed sales information including costumer information, equipment and payment tracking, commission structures, and sales status. </li>
	<li class="content">Much Much More!</li>
</ul>
<p class="content">This is such a crucial aspect of Executive Suite.  As you use the Sale Management tool, you will find so many feature that you will love.  It is our hope that they will make you office life a lot simpler.</p>

<h2 class="subheader">Contact Management</h2>
<p class="content">This simple tool grew out our research into the life a Kirby Distributers Office.  As we watched offices receive numerous calls requesting in home demo or the free carpeting cleaning we realized that Distributers need a tool to handle all those customers they deal with on a daily basis.</p>

<h2 class="subheader">Reports</h2>
<p class="content">The following reports are included in the initial version of the beta software.</p>
<ul>
	<li class="content"><u>Inventory Report:</u>  Simple report used to showcase inventory by product type over a given date range</li>
	<li class="content"><u>General Sales Report:</u> Provides basic statistics about offices sales over a given time period</li>
	<li class="content"><u>Individual Sales Report:</u> Highlights important information pertaining to a specific sale. </li>
	<li class="content"><u>Direct Sales:</u> Generates a direct sales report for the given time frame</li>
	<li class="content"><u>General Commission Summary:</u>  Provides a break down of commissions paid to all dealers with respect to sales information</li>
	<li class="content"><u>Payroll Statement:</u> Break Down of Total Commission for each dealer for a given time period (pay period)</li>
	<li class="content"><u>Team Leader Daily Check In/Out:</u> Provides a list of all items currently checked out based on the Team Leader.</li>
</ul>


<h2 class="subheader">Admin</h2>

<p class="content">The heart of the program, this tool is used to establish rules and administrative functions for the entire program.</p>
<ul>
	<li class="content">Users: This section is used to store and create a list of all employee of the company.  Please use this section to create accounts for all your dealers, team leaders, canvassers, etc before using the programs.  Please note that while adding a user, you have the ability to select a permission rule for user.  While the permission security system is not fully integrated into this version beta software, please establish the proper permission not for easier use in the future.  Below is an explanation of the future expected permissions granted to each role.
	<ul>
		<li class="content"><u>Admin:</u> This is a unrestricted account with the ability to manipulate any aspects of the system.  We recommend the role for all office manager and distributer accounts. </li>
		<li class="content"><u>Super User:</u> This is a more limited version of the account.  Sensitive information for this account and certain editing and adding privileges have been removed.</li>
		<li class="content"><u>Read Only:</u> Has access to view all sections of the program but cannot add or edit anything.</li>
		<li class="content"><u>Restricted Users:</u> This role is recommend for Dealers/Canvassers/etc.  User granted this role is restricted to viewing information prevalent to them such as their personal payroll statement.  This role is not currently available in the application.  Expect to see it on a future demo update.  </li>
	</ul>
	<li class="content">Teams: Used to display and create sales teams.  </li>
	<li class="content">Products and Accessories: Create/Display products and accessories types that your offices sells.</li>
	<li class="content">Office and Storage Locations: Display and create office and storage locations for inventory tracking purposes.</li>
	<li class="content">Finance Institutions: Used in connection with Adding a Sales, this tool allows for creating new financing options for your costumers and establishing the rules for these institutions.  </li>
	<li class="content">Commission templates: Add the most common commissions used my your office to pay your dealers and canvassers.  Commission template are then used when adding a sale to easily pay commissions to those involved in the sale.    </li>
	<li class="content">Tax Rates: Used in connection with the Add Sales Tool, this allows for the creation of sales tax rules for individual counties in your area.  Please create sales tax rules for your areas before starting to use this program.</li>
</ul>
<p class="content">Again we thank you for participating in the beta program of Executive Suite.  With your help we can make this the perfect tool for your office.  Please feel free to contact us anytime at support@esuite.republictech.net with any feedback on your beta experience.  As the beta progresses, we will update Executive Suite with new and exciting features.  We will inform you of the new features right here.  </p>

